product.title: Kawaii Small Tato Surfing Tee
product.body_html:
Glide your way through life!

Go on a journey with Tato and ride your wave. You never know the next wave can take you to a beautiful location whilst you carve out an elegant journey. But it could also send you through a wild ride and go through an extraordinary experience before you finally reach your goal. Something everyone should try out! Whether that's a new job, a new activity or hobby or even making new friends.

Conquer your fear and take a leap of faith with Tato and ride your wave, OWN IT! This tee is suitable for all genders and ages above the age of 6.

Details

  • 200 g/m²
  • Made from 100% Cotton
  • Part of Collection 2 Design 2
  • Crew neck design
  • Short sleeve


Choose between seven different sizes and two different tee colors. We always recommend going 1 size up.

Heat Transfer Printing Technology
Heat transfer printing uses the process of heat to transfer an image created in wax to an object or garment. This printing method is compatible with pre-painted images on a wax sheet or can be used to create an image by layering wax dye onto an object.

All printing methods have different advantages that they bring to the table. Heat transfer printing is widely used as it creates durable, heat resistant, adhesive and water-resistant designs. Additionally, the colours created in the image are high resolution with bright and bold colours.


Care & washing pointers

  • Wash less
  • Wash with similar colours
  • Wash cold
  • Wash (and dry) inside out
  • Use the right (amount of) detergents
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron on reverse
  • Store correctly
  • Treat stains immediately!
